						               													<description>The Angel Wars strategy board game is simple to learn.  Yet, it has a depth of strategy that is fascinating to players of all levels.  The game features the excellent art and intriguing characters from the amazing animated series, Angel Wars.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game begins with the game tiles set up in checkerboard design.  You control the 6 guardian angels.  Your opponent controls the 6 demons (or the 6 messenger angels if your opponent prefers not to play the demons).  Players take turns moving, following the rules of movement, until one player has successfully moved all of his/her pieces to the opposite sides of the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;However, it&amp;rsquo;s not that simple.  You can only move your piece on a tile of matching color.  Players flip tiles to match their piece.  You must find a way to clear a path for both your blue pieces and your orange pieces while trying to block your opponent&amp;rsquo;s pieces in the process.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Offering two styles of play, this game is sure to become a favorite among game players of all ages and skill levels.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
